Name: This War of Mine: The Little Ones

Achievements.Name: War is over
Achievements.Description: The dogs of war have been raging around for so long. I survived and I hope I am not the only one.

Achievements.Name: Day 7
Achievements.Description: Weâ€™ve been holed up here for seven days, and weâ€™ve managed to keep everyone alive - so far...

Achievements.Name: Vexing snow
Achievements.Description: Vexing snow. Half of the cityâ€™s buried so deep we can't get there. My kingdom for a snow plow...

Achievements.Name: Finished ransacking
Achievements.Description: We've explored every nook and cranny of our abode. Now we must venture outside for more supplies.

Achievements.Name: Bless the radio
Achievements.Description: The radio is useful beyond expectations. We get weather reports, important news and music too.

Achievements.Name: Distilled gold
Achievements.Description: We managed to distill some moonshine. Under siege, food and alcohol are always in high demand.

Achievements.Name: Doubled the watch
Achievements.Description: It's crucial to secure our place against intruders. Two lookouts can watch out for each other.

Achievements.Name: Miraculous recovery
Achievements.Description: Either modern medicines work miracles, or perhaps some of us have really robust immune systems.

Achievements.Name: Patched up and ready to go
Achievements.Description: What good fortune. We managed to dress these grave wounds and now they are healing nicely.

Achievements.Name: Back from the brink
Achievements.Description: With just kind words and deeds, we helped one of us survive the darkest depression.

Achievements.Name: Hostel's open!
Achievements.Description: We now have enough beds for everyone except the one who has to go out and scavenge.

Achievements.Name: Shooting for five stars
Achievements.Description: For the first time since we wound up here all of us ate a hot meal. Let's not get used to it yet.

Achievements.Name: First blood
Achievements.Description: One of us had a brush with violent death. Letâ€™s hope thereâ€™ll be no more such encounters.

Achievements.Name: Creature comforts
Achievements.Description: Our place is starting to resemble a proper home and it keeps the spirits up.

Achievements.Name: Traces of lives
Achievements.Description: Every building we visit has a story to tell. What kind of story will we leave behind...?

Achievements.Name: We have wintered
Achievements.Description: The winter's gone. The freeze is over. We made it through... everyone made it! Amazing.

Achievements.Name: We made it!
Achievements.Description: At first we hardly dared to hope weâ€™d make it, yet we're still here. It means somethingâ€¦ right?

Achievements.Name: We've been everywhere
Achievements.Description: We've searched everywhere, and thereâ€™s almost nothing useful left. This war can't end soon enough.

Achievements.Name: We made a stand
Achievements.Description: Bandits came in packs like hungry wolves. We beat them back every night. And everyone survived.

Achievements.Name: A bit of indulgence
Achievements.Description: We all indulged our addictions. It keeps the spirits up, and to hell with health issues for once!

Achievements.Name: The school of life
Achievements.Description: Itâ€™s crucial that kids learn to survive on their own. What if we donâ€™t come back one night?

Achievements.Name: Our future
Achievements.Description: We made it! Schools will reopen soon. From now on, kids will live a normal life again.

Achievements.Name: Avoid the worst
Achievements.Description: Attacking a place that shelters a kidâ€¦ Atrocious! We stand together to protect our little one!

Achievements.Name: Better days
Achievements.Description: Kidsâ€¦ they sometimes seem to be far away from this war. Itâ€™s heartwarming.

Achievements.Name: Bond for life
Achievements.Description: At least the kid has a new playmate. Maybe it will even be a break from our daily routine here.

Achievements.Name: Everybodyâ€™s got to learn
Achievements.Description: Solidarity. Thatâ€™s the first thing we have to teach to our children.

Achievements.Name: Our own playground
Achievements.Description: We wish we could be kids again and have fun with practically nothing.

Achievements.Name: No more tears
Achievements.Description: Nothing is more beautiful to see than a child smile and play again.
